            },
            {
              "text": "If the power stopped the garden would die and the life would end soon, leaving only still.",
              "audioStart": 47.775,
              "audioEnd": 52.15
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo and Maya knew they had to repair the ship power very soon to keep the garden alive.",
              "audioStart": 53.013,
              "audioEnd": 57.413
            },
            {
              "text": "They saw a damage panel near the garden that needed a quick fix before the temperature dropped further.",
