              "audioStart": 73.888,
              "audioEnd": 78.338
            },
            {
              "text": "The wires were loose and the power still could not flow to the garden because of the broken clamp.",
              "audioStart": 79.2,
              "audioEnd": 83.787
            },
            {
              "text": "If they tightened the wires the power would flow and the garden would live again as the people hoped.",
              "audioStart": 84.65,
              "audioEnd": 89.312
            },
            {
              "text": "They fixed the panel and the power began to rise slowly, making the whole ship interior bright.",
              "audioStart": 90.175,
              "audioEnd": 95.263
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The garden lights glow brighter and the plants began to grow very fast, covering the floor with green.",
              "audioStart": 96.125,
              "audioEnd": 101.412
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo and Maya felt a sense of hope as they watched the life rise still, feeling proud.",
              "audioStart": 102.275,
